column5: Three-bedroom house with large, shady yard and simple, stylish furnishings.  Perfectly situated in East Kessler Park, just a mile from the adorable Bishop Arts District and quick access to Downtown and Uptown Dallas. A few blocks from the paved Kessler Park Trail, perfect for a jog or bike ride.  Great for couples, families, or other small groups.
column8: Whole House, Shady Yard, Near Bishop Arts
